kits for use in reciprocating and gas turbine generator set markets power modules single double and triple axel tow behind trailers with optional integral double wall fuel tanks and fuel tanks with various capacities the company also provides load banks that are used in testing electrical power sources electrical control panels and equipment circuit breakers which are used for engines generators pumps and fuel level contr professional power products inc designs manufactures and sells custom engineered integrated electrical power generation systems it offers enclosure products including drop over style weatherproof and sound attenuated enclosures as well as field erection kits for use in reciprocating and gas turbine generator set markets power modules single double and triple axel tow behind trailers with optional integral double wall fuel tanks and fuel tanks with various capacities the company also provides load banks that are used in testing electrical power sources electrical control panels and equipment circuit breakers which are used for engines generators pumps and fuel level control and switchgears that are used for distribution paralleling and motor control applications in utility industrial and critical power industries in addition it offers a range of engineering design and consulting support technical support and installation services the company’s products have applications in utility offshore oil and gas platforms hospitals and electrical products and systems as well as in diesel and natural gas power generation markets professional power products inc was founded in  and is headquartered in darien wisconsin as of april   professional power products inc operates as a subsidiary of power solutions international inc detailed description  west madison streetdarien wi united statesfounded in  phone  fax  wwwprofessionalpowerproductscom key executives for professional power products inc professional power products inc does not have any key executives recorded professional power products inc key developments power solutions international inc signs new supply deal jun   power solutions international inc announced that its wholly owned subsidiary professional power products inc pi has signed a supply agreement valued at just over  million pi designs manufactures and sells customengineered integrated electrical generation systems for the demand response microgrid combined heat and power chp and standbyprime power markets under the agreement terms pi will supply highly customized power generation systems to a major integrated energy solution provider with shipments beginning in the third quarter of  and concluding in the first quarter of  the agreement represents pis first large distributed generation order and illustrates pis custom design capabilities this is a significant win for pi that demonstrates the value of the unique synergies between pi and psi sterling and wilson pvt ltd selects power solutions international inc and professional power products inc to supply engines and packaging services dec   power solutions international inc psi and its wholly owned subsidiary professional power products inc pi has been selected by sterling and wilson pvt ltd sw to supply engines and packaging services for the rapidly expanding north american cogenerationcombined heat and power chp market through sterling and wilson cogen solutions llc swcs swcs will initially open offices in chicago philadelphia and new york with plans to expand into other regions as the market continues to grow swcs’s goal is to become the dominant player in the cogeneration market by providing companies with the customized products and services they desire through the combined capabilities of sw pi and psi swcs will supply development engineering product construction service and financing of chp systems making it the only company in the market that can internally control all aspects of such projects sterling and wilson cogen solutions is already pursuing several chp projects and will be certifying cogeneration systems in both state and department of energy programs similar private companies by industry company name region c technologies inc united states m technologies inc united states dc inc united states  electrical llc united states d energetics inc united states recent private companies transactions typedate target no transactions available in the past  months request profile update   the information and data displayed in this profile are created and managed by sp global market intelligence a division of sp global bloombergcom does not create or control the content for inquiries please contact sp global market intelligence directly by clicking here stock quotes market data is delayed at least  minutes company lookup most searched private companies company name geographic region lawyers committee for civil rights under law united states nyc inc united states the advertising council inc united states bertelsmann ag europe rush university united states sponsored financial commentaries sponsored links browse companies a b c d e f g h i j k l m n o p q r s t u v w x y z              request profile update only a company representative may request an update for the company profile documentation will be required to contact professional power products inc please visit wwwprofessionalpowerproductscom company data is provided by sp global market intelligence please use this form to report any data issues information missing  please enter your information in the following fields company name your name your email address your phone number type of data overview executives key developments similar companies transactions update needed all data changes require verification from public sources please include the correct value or values and a source where we can verify cancel submit your requested update has been submitted our data partners will research the update request and update the information on this page if necessary resea